headline: UnitedHealth Under Fire as Medicaid & Centene Bombshell Rattle Sector
summary: UNH and peers tumble as Medicaid cuts, enrollment shifts and rising costs shake up the managed care sector.

headline: UnitedHealth Remains Largest U.S. Insurer By Market Cap After 40% Hit In Q2 2025
summary: UnitedHealth continued to be the largest US insurer by market capitalization during the second quarter, even as it experienced a historic tumble as investors balked at earnings figures.

headline: The Villages Health ("TVH") Announces Strategic Restructuring and Agreement to be Acquired by CenterWell
summary: The Villages Health ("TVH"), the trusted healthcare system for The Villages retirement community in Florida, today announced that it is proceeding with a strategic restructuring to preserve the business's day-to-day operations and further enhance patient care.
